<section class=" section--shadow hero-banner hero-banner--faq">
	<div class="overlay">
		<div class="content">
			<h1 class="title carter white fs--60">
				Frequently Asked Questions			</h1>
			<p class="text white fs--16">
				Here, you can find the answers to some interesting questions we received.			</p>
			<div class="button-container">
				<a href="/about" data-scroll class="resetlink button button--white" title="About Flüüfff">
					About Flüüfff				</a>
				<a href="/register/terms" data-scroll class="resetlink button button--white" title="Rules & policies">
					Rules & Policies				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>




<section class="section section--padding about-overview section--shadow">
	<div class="flex-container">
					<div class="flex-half">
									<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">Can we help you with the convention?</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								Of course! You can send us an email at <a href="mailto:contact@fluufff.org">contact@fluufff.org</a> and we’ll look into it.
	<br/>
	But the best way to support the Flüüfff is simply to attend it!							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
											<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">How can I pay for drinks and extras at the hotel?</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								The hotel accepts cash, debit and credit cards (Visa).							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
											<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">Does the hotel have a car park?</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								Yes! And it’s free for all attendees!							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
											<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">I’m allergic to a specific kind of food, what do I do?</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								Please inform us! When filling your registration form, tell us about your specific food allergies. We’ll pass the info to the hotel and information about allergenic food will be present near the buffet dishes.							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
											<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">My budget for food is a bit tight, what can I do?</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								Breakfast and dinner are included in the con fee. There will be two large buffets per day and drinks (water, juices, soft drinks, wine and table beer) are also included in them.
	<br/>
	The lunch is up to you but no worries! The two meals will be served till late and will be pretty filling.
	<br/>
	The crew will gladly give you directions to the nearest grocery stores in Blankenberge so you can make “budgeted”, yet delicious, meals.							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
											<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">What payment methods do you accept?</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								We accept bank transfers, credit or debit cards. If you can’t pay with any of this payment method, please contact <a href="mailto:registration@fluufff.org">registration@fluufff.org</a>							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
										</div>

							<div class="flex-half">
									<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">Can I bring my animal with me?</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								Sadly, the hotel doesn’t allow any pets.
<br/>
Service dogs are of course always allowed on the hotel premises. Please inform us upon registration about bringing a service dog. We will make the necessary arrangements with the hotel to meet your request. Please note that extra fees might be charged <span class="highlight">by the hotel</span> (extra cleaning, mandatory single room). Make sure you inform us and we’ll be pleased to help you.							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
											<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">Does the hotel have wifi?</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								Yes! Free wifi everywhere!							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
											<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">What and where do we eat?</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								Breakfast and dinner are included in the price of the convention.
	<br/>
	They consist in two large buffets accessible in the hotel’s restaurant.
	<br/>
	Breakfast will be served from 07:30 till 9:30 on weekdays and from 8:00 till 10:00 on weekend.
	<br/>
	Dinner will be serverd from 18:00 till 19:30							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
											<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">I’m vegetarian or vegan, is that a problem?</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								Of course not! Make sure to inform us upon registration. Every meal at the hotel will propose vegetarian and vegan alternatives.							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
											<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">Can I make partial payments?</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								Yes! You can pay in up to 3 installments. Your first payment must be at least 120€. Your last installment must arrive 2 months after your registration has been accepted.							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
											<div class="faq__item">
						<div class="faq__item--inner">
							<h2 class="title fs--18 lnh-150 blue carter question">I’d like to try another restaurant.</h2>
							<p class="text fs--16 answer">
								No problem either! Blankenberge is a pretty touristic city with plenty of shops and restaurants. Simply ask the staff for advice and directions and they’ll help you.							</p>
						</div>
						</div>
										</div>

						</div>
</section>



